			<h2 class="title"><a href="http://allthingsd.com/20131203/calling-overseas-on-wi-fi/" id="epost-376493" class="post-link">Calling Overseas on Wi-Fi</a></h2>
							<p class="byline">
					<a href="http://allthingsd.com/author/walt/" rel="author">Walt Mossberg</a> in <a href="http://allthingsd.com/category/mossbergs-mailbox/">Mossberg&#8217;s Mailbox</a> on December 3, 2013 at 6:18 pm PT				</p>
						Walt Mossberg answers a reader&#8217;s question about using Wi-Fi to make international calls.		</div><!--.excerpt-text-->
